div.div: Add work-life balance resources including nurturing relationships, prioritizing personal time, seeking support, setting boundaries, and time management strategies
Add technology toolkit with various developer tools and resources

Add resource links for various industries including finance, healthcare, hospitality, manufacturing, marketing, real estate, and retail
- Created finance.ts with links to financial tools and resources. - Created healthcare.ts with links to healthcare tools and resources. - Created hospitality.ts with links to hospitality management tools. - Created manufacturing.ts with links to manufacturing software and tools. - Created marketing.ts with a comprehensive list of marketing platforms and tools. - Created real-estate.ts with links to real estate platforms and services. - Created retail.ts with links to retail management and e-commerce solutions.

Refactors leadership tools for updated industry focus
Replaces existing leadership tools with new entries that reflect current industry sectors, including technology, healthcare, finance, education, retail, manufacturing, hospitality, energy, marketing, and real estate.
Enhances descriptions and introductions to better align with industry-specific leadership challenges and growth areas.
Improves overall clarity and relevance of the tools for users seeking targeted leadership resources.

Extends mindfulness practices with new work-life balance interface
Adds a new interface for work-life balance scenarios, providing structured data for both work and life scenarios, along with reasoning and afterthoughts.
Updates existing mindfulness practices to enhance clarity and organization of the data structure.
Add WorkLifeBalanceCard component to display work-life balance information with dynamic content
Add ToolLinkCard component to display tool links with dynamic images and buttons
Refactor BehavioralActivitiesCard to use 'data' prop for consistency in data access
Add debug logging for corresponding tools in Layout component
Add ToolLinkCard and WorkLifeBalanceCard components to display tool data in mental health toolkit pages
Fix prop name in BehavioralActivitiesCard component for consistency
Add additional image hosts to remotePatterns for enhanced image loading support
Refactor BehavioralActivitiesCard to improve heading structure and add MindfulnessPractices interface for enhanced toolkit organization

Enhance mental health toolkit pages with tool information display
- Added subtitle and introduction rendering to various toolkit pages. - Removed unnecessary console logs from layout components. - Implemented data fetching for tool resources in multiple pages.
Removes debug console logs from Layout component to clean up code

Add mindfulness practices for sensory resets, daily check-ins, emotional responses, mood tracking, and breath anchoring techniques
- Implemented various mindfulness practices including sensory resets (temperature contrast, taste-based grounding, weighted object reset, etc.) to enhance emotional regulation. - Introduced daily check-in practices (morning self-scan, emotional temperature check, gratitude snapshot, etc.) to promote self-awareness and emotional intelligence. - Added techniques for responding instead of reacting (pause practice, mindful listening, cognitive reframing, etc.) to improve emotional responses. - Created mood tracking methods (mood logging, mood trigger journal, mood-event correlation chart, etc.) to identify emotional patterns and triggers. - Developed breath anchoring techniques (box breathing, 4-7-8 breathing, diaphragmatic breathing, etc.) to enhance focus and reduce anxiety.
Removes unused breathing techniques layout and page components to streamline the mental health toolkit section
Removes debug console logs from Layout component to clean up code
Adds BehavioralActivitiesCard component and updates mental health toolkit page to display activities; refines BehavioralActivities interface for better type safety.
Enhances accessibility statement page by updating content to reflect commitment to inclusivity; adds structured accessibility measures and guidelines for improved user experience.
Enhances events and workshops page by adding a featured image gallery and updating layout for improved user experience; introduces new image data for gallery display.
Removes unused LogoCloud import from About page to streamline code
Refines About page content to emphasize well-being as a foundation for impact and updates statistics to reflect lives impacted through wellness programs.
